abstract: >-
  Model Maker is a free, open-source offline AI assistant for emergency,
  medical, and survival situations. It runs 100% on the user's device with
  no internet required, supporting 29 languages with Arabic and English
  as primary languages. Powered by Qwen2.5 GGUF models with ONNX-based
  RAG for medical knowledge retrieval.
